      • getKeyValuePairIterator

        public static final TemplateHashModelEx2.KeyValuePairIterator getKeyValuePairIterator(TemplateHashModelEx hash)
                                                                               throws TemplateModelException
        TemplateHashModelExKeyValuePairIterator that even works for a non-TemplateHashModelEx2 TemplateHashModelEx. This is used to simplify code that needs to iterate through the key-value pairs of TemplateHashModelEx-s, as with this you don't have to handle non-TemplateHashModelEx2-s separately. For non-TemplateHashModelEx2 values the iteration will throw TemplateModelException if it reaches a key that's not a string (TemplateScalarModel).
        抛出:
        TemplateModelException
